snippet.title: Baahubali: The Game (2017) Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Mahishmati needs your help! Train your army, build your defences, and join forces with Baahubali, Kattappa and the other heroes of Mahishmati to push back the ruthless Kalakeya. 

Baahubali: The Game is an action-packed real-time strategy game based on S. S. Rajamouli’s Baahubali movie series developed by Moonfrog in partnership with Arka Media and Graphics India. The game is proudly made in India and made for India.

Download the Game:
Android/ Google PlayStore - https://goo.gl/Ap2wfN

Stay Connected:
https://www.facebook.com/BaahubaliTheGame/

About Moonfrog:
Moonfrog Labs is India’s fastest growing gaming company focused on making mobile games for the Indian subcontinent. The executive team has deep gaming and technology experience from companies like Zynga, Electronic Arts, Google and Microsoft. Moonfrog Labs has developed several hit mobile games including 'Teen Patti Gold', 'Bingo Club', 'Smash Cricket' and Alia Bhatt: Star Life, of which the hugely popular 'Teen Patti Gold’ is on the list of top five highest-grossing games in India on both Android and iOS.

Also, download Teen Patti Gold: 
taps.io/tpg

http://moonfroglabs.com/
https://www.facebook.com/moonfroglabs/
https://twitter.com/MoonfrogLabs
